                    <h2 class="section-heading">Track Your Code in Real Time</h2>
                        <br>
                    <p class="lead">Code Union is a dashboard that provides your development team with a real-time feed from Github, Pivotal Tracker, Travis CI and Code Climate that lets you gauge quality of your code and the speed of your project</p>
</p>
