                    <h2 class="section-heading">Let Clients/Managers See What's Going On</h2>
                        <br>                    
                        <p class="lead">Unlike UI/UX projects, backend development lives in a cloud somewhere between a laptop, github and project management software like Pivtoal Tracker, Rally and Basecamp. Code Union gives your projects a home where progress is easily tracked in a public forum and wins are able to be celebrated by the team </p>
                </div>
