                    <hr class="section-heading-spacer">
                    <div class="clearfix"></div>
                    <h2 class="section-heading">Mobile Ready</h2>
                        <br>
                    <p class="lead">Code Union monitors your codes vital signs. Don’t wait, see it live on a business dashboard as it happens. Focus on what’s important and allow decsion makers to see progress being made in real time.<br><br>
                    Becasue we are mobile ready, you can check your progjects stats on the go.</p>
